These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There 2 different types of food: pear, lettuce
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, fonseca
The people have 2 different jobs:  doctor, librarian
There are 2 different nationalities: french, indian
1. the indian is on the left or right of the librarian##3
2. the person eating lettuce is in an even position##4
3. the fonseca-smoker is the person eating pear##1
4. the indian is on the right of the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Food      | pear  | lettuce   |
| Cigar   | fonseca     | pall-mall   |
| Job         | librarian | doctor |
| Nationality     | french | indian    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
House: farmhouse, victorian
The people have 2 different jobs:  librarian, engineer
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: handball, parkour
City: hannover, nizza
1. the person who's sport is parkour is in an odd position##4
2. the librarian is the person traveling to nizza##1
3. the victorian house is on the right of the engineer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| House          | farmhouse     | victorian |
| Job   | engineer | librarian  |
| Sport           | parkour         | handball     |
| City     | hannover   | nizza    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
There 2 different types of food: pumpkin, grapes
House: colonial, gothic-revival
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, june
City: new-york, venice
1. the person traveling to venice is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
3. the person eating pumpkin is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Food    | grapes     | pumpkin |
| House         | gothic-revival | colonial    |
| Birthday         | march         | june        |
| City   | new-york         | venice    |

