.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: documentary, martial-arts
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, lacrosse
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, snowmobile
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: sunflower, begonia
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
3. the person who growsbegonia is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Movie-Genre      | martial-arts     | documentary |
| Sport          | lacrosse   | golf  |
| Transport         | skateboard | snowmobile     |
| Flower   | sunflower  | begonia         |

