.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-5::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, taxi
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, dancing
2 different games are played: scrabble, snooker
There are 2 different nationalities: italian, malaysian
1. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
2. the malaysian is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Transport      | bike | taxi       |
| Hobby           | dancing      | filmmaking     |
| Game   | snooker       | scrabble   |
| Nationality           | malaysian          | italian |

