.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: time-travel, family
2 different games are played: scrabble, chess
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: june, february
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: country, rock
1. the fan of rock is in an even position##4
2. the person playing chess is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person watching family movies is the person playing scrabble##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre           | family | time-travel    |
| Game   | scrabble       | chess |
| Birthday           | june         | february    |
| Music-Genre         | country    | rock   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-7::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, august
There are 2 different favourite colors: fuchsia, mauve
2 different pets are kept: hamster, guinea-pig
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, begonia
1. the person who likes fuchsia is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
3. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the person who likes fuchsia##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Birthday      | august    | march   |
| Color          | fuchsia     | mauve |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | hamster     |
| Flower   | balloon-flower       | begonia     |

