There are 2 different favourite colors: red, blood-red
There 2 different types of food: tomato, cherry
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, march
1. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
2. the person eating tomato is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
3. the person who's birthday is in september is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Movie-Genre    | spy | action    |
| Color         | blood-red        | red |
| Food         | tomato          | cherry     |
| Birthday   | september        | march     |

 